{"tid":640843,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"涉打前女友　男警被捕","createTime":"2018-04-24T14:44:53.000Z","updateTime":"2018-04-24T20:11:44.000Z","uid":30647,"like":10,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"e1b7b01a840ade314bc07e618acf17769b4bbfb3","tid":640843,"uid":30647,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-24T14:44:53.000Z","msg":"又有警員涉知法犯法。一名24歲姓黃女子去年11月報案指，被擔任警員的35歲姓余前男友，分別在去年6月、7月及10月用手襲擊，警方經調查及徵詢法律意見後拘捕余，控以其3項「襲擊致造成實際身體傷害」罪名。案件將於下周一（30日）在九龍城裁判法院提堂，案件交由黃大仙警區重案組第1隊跟進。<br />\n<br />\n警方重申，警隊非常重視人員的操守，任何人員干犯違法行為，警隊絕不容忍和姑息，定必嚴正處理，進行刑事調查及紀律覆檢。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.mingpao.com/ins/instantnews/web_tc/article/20180424/s00001/1524579211161\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fins%2Finstantnews%2Fweb_tc%2Farticle%2F20180424%2Fs00001%2F1524579211161&d=as9LQJ0q1zqmooOgAV5qMJWUQYxlHU4vp7GM3pu%2FB4U%3D&h=1eb950c6\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fins%2Finstantnews%2Fweb_tc%2Farticle%2F20180424%2Fs00001%2F1524579211161&h=b6bc3ea6\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.mingpao.com/ins/instantnews/web_tc/article/20180424/s00001/1524579211161</a>"},{"pid":"28c0d38854bba8abecab338d4fed407407483bbf","tid":640843,"uid":20867,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-24T14:46:36.000Z","msg":"抵打"},{"pid":"6600b19ea2926a3c5ff522b8fa2be1ef0db50369","tid":640843,"uid":5195,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-24T14:54:11.000Z","msg":"警方重申，警隊非常重視人員的操守，任何人員干犯違法行為，警隊絕不容忍和姑息，定必嚴正處理，進行刑事調查及紀律覆檢。"},{"pid":"bcb4b5678c306f2a2e113a9b3ecb141ed49a74a6","tid":640843,"uid":144883,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-24T14:57:14.000Z","msg":"唔驚，黑警工會會籌錢幫你打官司<br />\n<br />\n下次醒d，打埋佢老母"},{"pid":"436a1a54f8035b3f8fa3442f697ac52dc4322860","tid":640843,"uid":13724,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"bcb4b5678c306f2a2e113a9b3ecb141ed49a74a6","tid":640843,"uid":144883,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"cited